# Dialer V2 Project Work-Flow (Block Diagram)

## System Block Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph AgentSide["Agent Side"]
        UI["Portal UI (Browser + JsSIP)"]
    end

    subgraph ControlPlane["Control Plane"]
        AUTH["auth-api"]
        AIO["dialer-aio (ESL + Routing Engine)"]
        REDIS["Redis (presence, pools, locks, callroute)"]
        RMQ["RabbitMQ (outbound jobs)"]
    end

    subgraph MediaPlane["Media / SIP Plane"]
        FS["FreeSWITCH"]
        CARRIER["Carrier / DID / SIP Trunk"]
    end

    UI -->|"Login"| AUTH
    AUTH -->|"SIP config + token"| UI
    UI <-->|"SIP WS/WSS register + call signaling"| FS

    FS -->|"ESL events: CHANNEL_*"| AIO
    AIO -->|"ESL commands: bridge/uuid_*"| FS

    AIO <-->|"agent state + pools + locks"| REDIS
    RMQ -->|"outbound call payload"| AIO
    CARRIER <-->|"inbound/outbound SIP calls"| FS
```

## Call Routing Block Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    IN["Inbound DID / Loopback / Outbound Job"] --> FS1["FreeSWITCH Dialplan"]
    FS1 --> TAG["Set call_type, call_role, route_group"]
    TAG --> PARK["Park Customer Leg"]
    PARK --> EVT["dialer-aio receives CHANNEL_PARK"]
    EVT --> PICK["Pick + lock agent from Redis pool"]
    PICK --> BRIDGE["Bridge to sofia/internal/${extension}%${sipDomain}"]
    BRIDGE --> ANSWER{"Agent answers?"}
    ANSWER -->|No| RETRY["Cooldown + retry next attempt"]
    RETRY --> PICK
    ANSWER -->|Yes| LIVE["Active bridged call"]
    LIVE --> END["Hangup / Normal clearing"]
    END --> CLEAN["Release locks, update route/disposition"]
```
